## Answer 3 — Missing Dates in Sequence

WITH RECURSIVE dates AS (
SELECT MIN(attend_date) AS dt
FROM Attendance
UNION ALL
SELECT DATE_ADD(dt, INTERVAL 1 DAY)
FROM dates
WHERE dt < (SELECT MAX(attend_date) FROM Attendance)
)
SELECT dt AS missing_date
FROM dates
WHERE dt NOT IN (
    SELECT attend_date FROM Attendance
);
```

