## Answer 5 — 2 Consecutive Salary Drops
WITH cte AS (
SELECT emp_id,
       month,
       salary,
       LAG(salary,1) OVER(
           PARTITION BY emp_id
           ORDER BY month
       ) prev1,
       LAG(salary,2) OVER(
           PARTITION BY emp_id
           ORDER BY month
       ) prev2
FROM SalaryHistory
)
SELECT DISTINCT emp_id
FROM cte
WHERE salary < prev1
  AND prev1 < prev2;
```

